snippet.title: Youtubers Life: OMG Edition | HD Trailer | Upcoming Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
(New) Active Giveaway
* $10 eShop Gift Card
* Ends 28th October 2018
* As channel grows so does the giveaway
Enter to Win : https://goo.gl/vYS6Hx

Youtubers Life: OMG Edition in work for Switch, planned for November 14.

About this game:
Youtubers Life is the ultimate life simulation game in which you can become the most successful youtuber on the planet! Create videos, get subscribers, attend events, interact with your fans… and grow your channel.

You will launch your new venture from your parents’ house and gain your first subscribers, views and likes, but soon you’re well on your way to fame and fortune as a popular influencer. Meet other well-known youtubers, go to the wildest parties, share your life through social media and deal with your haters. Monetize your content, sign with exclusive networks and customize your place with the coolest stuff. Grow until you can afford a mansion in outer space!

Follow your passion to success in one of three channels, or all of them!

✦SPECIAL Giveaway✦ (Active)
3 x $20 Nintendo eShop Gift Card (Worldwide)
Enter to win : https://goo.gl/zhNRvw

✦NEW Switch games ANNOUNCED✦
Check here: https://goo.gl/FAj3Xz

*BEST Upcoming Switch RACING :
 https://youtu.be/6QKlt-YpU7Y

*BEST Upcoming ADVENTURE Switch : 
https://youtu.be/hmuNznOfULY

*BEST Upcoming Switch RPG : 
https://youtu.be/8r6roU2PVh8
